Proposed law authorizes the commissioner to require submission of claims-level data,
including but not limited to reimbursement amounts, dispensing fees, and any adjustments,
for the purpose of verifying compliance with proposed law.
Proposed law provides that the provisions of proposed law shall be given prospective and
retroactive application.
